Cape Canaveral Air Force Station Launch.label: Cape Canaveral Air Force Station Launch Complex 19
Cape Canaveral Air Force Station Launch.description: Launch Complex 19 is a deactivated launch site on Cape Canaveral Air Force Station, Florida used by NASA to launch all of the Gemini manned spaceflights. It was also used by unmanned Titan I and Titan II launch vehicles. Wikipedia

Cape Canaveral Air Force Station Launch.label: Cape Canaveral Air Force Station Launch Complex 34
Cape Canaveral Air Force Station Launch.description: Cape Canaveral Air Force Station Launch Complex 34 is a launch site on Cape Canaveral, Florida. Cape Canaveral Air Force Station Launch.label: Cape Canaveral Air Force Station Launch Complex 5

Cape Canaveral Air Force Station Launch.description: Launch Complex 14 is a launch site at Cape Canaveral Air Force Station, Florida. Cape Canaveral Air Force Station Launch.label: Cape Canaveral Air Force Station Launch Complex 13
